al million years) to attain the explosion after the\nabove mentioned conditions cease to keep stable the WD. Therefore it is\npractically impossible to detect the trace of the exploding WD companion in\nrecent pre-explosion frames of even very near SN Ia.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Apr 2013 10:14:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-30"}
